name: Nike Air Max 270
description: The Nike Air Max 270 is the first lifestyle Air Max from Nike, offering style, comfort, and plenty of attitude. The design with the large window and various fresh colors is inspired by Nike's legendary and incredibly innovative Air Max shoes.

name: Adidas Ultraboost 20
description: The Adidas Ultraboost 20 is designed for athletes who demand high performance and style. Featuring Adidas' innovative Boost technology, these shoes provide unparalleled energy return with every step. The sleek design and variety of color options make them a versatile choice for any activity.
